latestIgtvVideos.title: Eating RGF for 4 Days in 4 Ways
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
💡 Spotlight Alert 💡

Y’all know we LOVE hearing how you eat and #BeRealGood...so we loved watching @thebresg try our products in four ways, in four days! 😎👏

Ever since Breanna got VSG surgery in August of 2020, she’s been focused on 
living a healthier lifestyle and finding foods that taste good AND are good for her. 🙌 And you can watch the whole video to learn which of our products were her absolute faves. 🤩

How many meals of RGF could you eat straight? 😉👇

latestIgtvVideos.title: Thanks for an amazing 3 years!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It’s been an epic 3 years, fam!! Our mission has always been to make nutritious food you can feel good about eating, and we’re so thankful you guys have embraced us on this journey — you are our motivation. 
We have some surprises in store for 2020 — and we are looking forward to another year with you. 
Cheers.
